name: Zeichnet die 8. Kriegsanleihe LCCN2004665979 - from Commons

desc.html: English:  Title: Zeichnet die 8. Kriegsanleihe Abstract: Poster shows a flying bell with wings; sunlight streams in the background. Text: I ring for war, I sing for victory. With an open hand, you will protect the land. Subscribe to the 8th War Loan. Physical description: 1 print (poster) : lithograph, color ; 60 x 44 cm. Notes: Forms part of: Rehse-Archiv für Zeitgeschichte und Publizistik.; Otto Lietz, München.; Title from item.
